<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en"
      xmlns:tal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/tal"
      xmlns:metal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/metal"
      metal:use-macro="base.macros['base']">

<tal:block metal:fill-slot="header-title">Authorize Application</tal:block>

<tal:block metal:fill-slot="content">

  <h1>Authorize application ${app.name}</h1>

  <p>The application <a href="${app.main_url}">${app.name}</a>
    is requesting access to the following items:</p>

  <ul>
    <li tal:repeat="scope scopes">${scope}</li>
  </ul>

  <p>You need to log in first and then you will be asked to
    authorize this application.</p>

  <p><a href="${request.route_url('oauth2_authorize_application', app=app._id)}">Ok, I'll log in</a></p>

</tal:block>

</html>
